    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "but what if that spark is gone for real? what if there's nothing left to wake up? it just feels like i'm dragging this heavy, empty thing around for no reason. it's exhausting to keep pretending there's something inside when it's clearly just... nothing. wouldn't it be more peaceful to just let the weight go?",
